#

Roasted Pumpkin Salad

45 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyEasy

Description

A warm, comforting salad featuring roasted pumpkin, fresh greens, and a tangy dressing for a delightful mix of flavors.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin: 2 cups, diced
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
